      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) احْذَرُوا عَوَاقِبَ الْعَثَرَاتِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Jameel Bin Salih who said, ",
          "‘Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> said: ‘Beware of the consequences of the slips (of the tongues)’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "22. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Jamil ibn Salih who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah (a.s.) has said, ‘Stay away from the consequences of slip and mistake (disregarding al-Taqiyyah’).’\"’ "
        ]
      }
